# Drizzle rules

## Schema
- Schema in `src/driven/drizzle/schema/schema.ts`. Use `odPdpSchema` from `schema-name.ts`.
- Domain enums (e.g. `Platform`) imported from `@domain/*` for consistency.

## Migrations
- Migrations in `src/driven/drizzle/schema/migrations/`.
- Config: `drizzle.config.ts`, `drizzle-test.config.ts`.
- Create: `pnpm migration:create <name>`. Check: `pnpm migration:check`.

## Repositories
- Implement `*RepositoryPort` from domain. Map DB rows → domain types.
- Repository tests: `src/driven/drizzle/*.repository.test.ts`. Use `test-db.fixtures.ts`, `uniquePostgresDatabase`.
